  "description": [
    "EverReady R j I IF your druggist or hardware dealer is sold out the new EverReady place your order now The new EverReady is the most sensational razor ever conceived Dollars added to the value but not one cent to the price Note the new frame and thank your lucky stars that blades like the Radio Steel exist and that 12 are in each dollar outfit Study the picture for the other features RADIO STEEL BLADES AT ALL DEALERS10 for 50c The EverReady is the most used razor in the world AMERICAN SAFETY RAZOR COMPANY Makers Brooklyn New York The 12 Radio Steel bladS in rash EVER READY Outfit mean 5 more and 12 better blades than in any other dollar safety razor Improved Frame and 12 Radio Steel Blades BIG BUBBLES MOW would you like to be able to blow a soap bubble as big as a trunk This has been accomplished by Dr Boys who has made them thirty inches in diameter With large bubbles of course many experi ments may be attempted that ari not feas ible with small ones The solution used is the well known Plateaus solution which consists of one part oleate of soda"
